EForm.Description: Used by web event to store/process supplier selection data received from SD

FieldEntry.Formula:
LET $checks := ARRAY( DB_LOOKUP( ARRAY("EFormType", "SD Request GUID"), "Procurement", "[RecordID] = " & N(HASH_GET([Params], "_recordId")) ), DB_LOOKUP( ARRAY("EFormType", "SD Request GUID"), "Quick Quote", "[RecordID] = " & N(HASH_GET([Params], "_recordId")) ) );
RETURN ARRAY_FIRST(ARRAY_WHERE($checks, $(i, item) ARRAY_INDEX($item, 2) <> NULL))

SetReturnValue.Description: Return 401 ( Unauthorised If Correlation ID DOES NOT MATCH )

ChangeFieldValues.Description: store supplier selection data and clear guid on PROCUREMENT (if Correlation ID MATCHES)
store supplier selection data and clear guid on QUICK QUOTE (if Correlation ID MATCHES)

SetReturnValue.ResultValueFormula: HASH( //this is a common format a lot of tools will understand "statusCode", 200, "body", HASH("message", "updated " & [Correlation EForm Match] & " ID: " & [Request Source RecordID]) )

ChangeFieldValues.Description: store supplier selection data on procurement

SetReturnValue.ResultValueFormula: HASH( //this is a common format a lot of tools will understand "statusCode", 200, "body", HASH("message", "updated procurement "&[Procurement RecordID]) )
